Detailed Description

cvmx_pci_cfg08

PCI_CFG08 = Ninth 32-bits of PCI config space (Base Address Register 2 - Low)

Description: BAR1: 2^39 (512GB) 64-bit Prefetchable Memory Space [0]: 0 (Memory Space) [2:1]: 2 (64bit memory decoder) [3]: 1 (Prefetchable) [31:4]: RAZ
